description: Recently sold: $199,000. Updated home nestled on 40 acres of beautiful pine and hardwood.  Remodeled Kitchen includes Corian countertops, new cupboards & tile backsplash.  The bay window in the Living Room prefectly frames the rolling hill views or sit on the deck and observe the abundant wildlife.  The main floor consists of a large entry, 3 spacious bedrooms with gorgeous hardwood floors, a full bath w/double sinks and wonderful tilework.  The lower level features the giant Master Bedroom with walk-in closet and ensuite bath with heated tile floor.  Finish the rest of the lower level to suite your needs.  Other great features include:  on demand water heater w/Mega Star water storage, newer furnace, 2 car garage, steel roof and the log siding blends perfectly with the wood setting.  This property borders Blandin and County lands on 3 sides. Plus your very own gravel pit.  Compliant Septic!
